&s;uddenly, &startq;I think 1 will go to him my|&s;elf;
&mdash;where is he?&endq;</P>
<P>Annette a&s;ked who was meant.</P>
<P>&startq;Signor Montoni,&endq; replied Emily,
&startq;I would &s;peak with him;&endq; and Annette,
now remembering the order he had given,
