<DIV3>
<HEAD>TO A SEA-NYMPH</HEAD>
<LG>
<L>O nymph! who loves to float on the green wave,</L>
<L>When Neptune &s;leeps beneath the moon-Iight hour,</L>
<L>Lull'd by thy mu&s;ic's melancholy pow'r,</L>
