</LG>
<Q><L>(Chorus)&mdash;<HI>Ari&s;e!</HI></L>
<L>(Semi-chorus)&mdash;<HI>Ari&s;e!</HI></L></Q>
<P>The la&s;t words being repeated by the
&s;urrounding group, the garland of flowers
was thrown into the waves, and the chorus,
&s;inking gradually into a chant, died away
in &s;ilence.</P>
<P>&startq;What can this mean, Maddelina?&endq; &s;aid
Emily, awakening from the plea&s;ing trance,
into which the mu&s;ie had lulled her.
&startq;This is the eve of a fe&s;tival, Signora,&endq;
replied Maddelina; &startq;and the pea&s;ants then
