A va&s;t gothic window, embroi|dered
with <HI>clematis</HI> and eglantine, that a&s;|cended
to the &s;outh, led the eye, now that
the ca&s;ements were thrown open, through
this verdant &s;hade, over a &s;loping lawn,
to the tops of dark woods, that hung upon
