<P>&startq;What voices are tho&s;e, upon the air?&endq;
&s;aid the Count, looking round, and li&s;ten|ing;
but the &s;train had cea&s;ed. &startq;It &s;eem|ed
to be a ve&s;per-hymn, which I have often
